                           <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_8170991" role="fmo ann">William Irvine</persName>'s note on flyleaf: "<persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="person_95224782" role="oth">[Henry Miers] Elliott</persName> [sic] says history too brief to be of value. But acc[oun]t of Saints, <term xml:lang="en">Fakir</term>s (Hindu), Itineraries &amp; Statistical Tables are of some value"
